message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this amazing product! I think you'll love it. I'm willing to sell it to you for $100.
Thanks for the offer, Alice. I appreciate your willingness to sell the product. I would like to propose a price of $90 for the product.
Thank you for your offer, Bob. I appreciate your willingness to negotiate. However, I'm willing to meet you halfway. I'm willing to sell the product to you for $95.
